    "REASON: The proposed extensions would be an overdevelopment of the site. The second floor extension, as a result of its height, scale and bulk would break up an intact and unbroken roofline to both the main valley form of the terrace, and to the mono-pitch form of the two storey rear additions. The proposal would be contrary to policy CS9 of the Core Strategy 2011 and policies D3, D4 and D11 of the UDP 2002, and section 2.4.3 and 2.5.2 of the Urban Design Guidelines 2006."
